---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'The AI-Powered Agile Blueprint';
const pageDescription = 'How I got rehired in 2 weeks after being laid off with thousands of other Scrum Masters. Get the free blueprint with my exact 3-phase roadmap.';
---

<LandingLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <!-- Hero Section - Two Column Layout Like FirstMovers -->
  <section class="bg-[#1a1a1a] min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32 sm:pb-24 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left Column - Text Content -->
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <!-- Personal intro -->
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 font-medium mb-6">
            Hi, I'm Danny.
          </p>

          <!-- Main Headline with "2 Weeks" highlighted -->
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] mb-8" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            <span class="text-white">How I Got Rehired in</span>
            <br />
            <span class="text-[#294bf3]">2 Weeks</span>
            <br />
            <span class="text-white">After Being Laid Off With Thousands of Other Scrum Masters</span>
          </h1>

          <!-- Hook statement -->
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-xl">
            When companies started cutting "ceremony-only" agile roles in January 2023, I built automation systems that proved I was technical—not "just a facilitator."
          </p>

          <!-- Value proposition -->
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white mb-10">
            This <span class="text-[#294bf3] font-semibold">free blueprint</span> is my exact 3-phase roadmap.
          </p>

          <!-- CTA Button -->
          <button
            type="button"
            data-modal-trigger="blueprint"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-12 sm:px-16 py-5 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#3d5af5] hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-10px_rgba(41,75,243,0.5)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#294bf3]/50"
          >
            Get The Blueprint
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column - Image/Visual -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
          <div class="relative w-full max-w-md lg:max-w-lg">
            <!-- Photo placeholder with professional styling -->
            <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gradient-to-br from-[#294bf3]/20 to-[#1a1a1a] rounded-2xl border-2 border-white/10 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
              <!-- Placeholder for Danny's photo -->
              <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-center p-8">
                  <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-[#294bf3]/30 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white/60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Photo of Danny</p>
                  <p class="text-white/30 text-xs mt-1">Replace with actual image</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Decorative elements -->
            <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-[#294bf3]/20 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-[#294bf3]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Crisis Story Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] leading-tight mb-12" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        My Layoff Should Have Been Career-Ending. Instead, I Was Back at Work in 2 Weeks.
      </h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#1a1a1a]/80 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
          In January 2023, companies made a choice:
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Keep the agile professionals who "just facilitated meetings" or keep the ones who "built technical systems."
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
          I was laid off along with thousands of other Scrum Masters. My peers spent months searching for interviews. Some are still looking.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a]">
          But I was back at work within two weeks—landing a Fortune 500 pharmaceutical role.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed font-bold text-[#1a1a1a]">
          The difference?
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
          In every interview, I could say:
        </p>
        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-[#294bf3] pl-6 py-2 my-8 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-r-lg">
          <p class="text-xl text-[#1a1a1a] italic">
            "I've built Jira automation systems that saved my last team 12 hours per sprint. I don't just coordinate work—I architect solutions that create measurable value."
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
          That's not facilitation. That's technical proof.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed font-bold text-[#294bf3]">
          So I made a different choice. I built systems that made me indispensable.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Inline Email Form Section -->
  <section class="bg-[#f0f7ff]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
            Get The AI-Powered Agile Blueprint
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-[#1a1a1a]/70">
            The 3-Phase Transformation: From Manual Coordinator to AI-Powered Architect
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Email Form - Pill style like FirstMovers -->
        <form class="mb-6">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-0 sm:border-2 sm:border-[#1a1a1a]/10 sm:rounded-full sm:p-2">
            <input
              type="email"
              placeholder="Enter your email"
              class="flex-1 px-6 py-4 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a]/10 sm:border-0 rounded-full sm:rounded-l-full text-lg text-[#1a1a1a] placeholder-[#1a1a1a]/40 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#294bf3] sm:focus:ring-0"
              required
            />
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#3d5af5] whitespace-nowrap"
            >
              Download The Blueprint
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>

        <!-- Social Proof -->
        <p class="text-center text-[#1a1a1a]/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          I've trained <strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">15,000+ agile professionals</strong> across 130 countries. This is the exact roadmap that creates career optionality—not just certifications.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof Statement Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] leading-tight mb-12 text-center" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        My Automation Systems Never Stop Working. They Don't Take Sick Days. They Just Create Value.
      </h2>

      <p class="text-xl text-[#1a1a1a]/80 leading-relaxed mb-10 text-center">
        While other Scrum Masters were updating Jira tickets manually, my automation systems were:
      </p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium text-lg">Syncing sprint dates automatically</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium text-lg">Prepping standup updates before meetings</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium text-lg">Flagging blockers 3 days before they became crises</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium text-lg">Sending stakeholder reports without human intervention</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I quickly realized this wasn't just about efficiency—it was about separating your value from your hours.
        </p>
        <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">
          Companies don't want coordinators anymore. They want architects who build systems.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Inside Section -->
  <section class="bg-[#f0f7ff]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Get My Career Survival Blueprint.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-[#1a1a1a]/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          This blueprint gives you the exact frameworks I built when my career was on the line. Inside, you'll get:
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA above frameworks -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <button
          type="button"
          data-modal-trigger="blueprint"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-12 sm:px-16 py-5 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#3d5af5] hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-10px_rgba(41,75,243,0.5)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#294bf3]/50"
        >
          I Need This Blueprint
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- 6 Framework Cards - 2x3 grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- Framework 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-[#1a1a1a]/5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">
                The 3-Phase Transformation Path
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#1a1a1a]/70 leading-relaxed">
                The exact career progression from Manual Coordinator → Automation Builder → Agentic Strategist → AI-Powered Architect. Includes time investment for each phase, skills to develop, and career impact at every stage.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-[#1a1a1a]/5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">
                The 5 Automation Patterns That Prove You're Technical
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#1a1a1a]/70 leading-relaxed">
                The Sprint Sync Engine, 12-Minute Standup, Stale Ticket Radar, and automated reporting systems that saved my teams 12+ hours per sprint—and got me hired in 2 weeks.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-[#1a1a1a]/5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">
                The Interview Answer Framework
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#1a1a1a]/70 leading-relaxed">
                The exact responses I used when interviewers asked "How do you ensure data accuracy?" and "How do you identify blockers early?" You'll sound technical, not like a meeting facilitator.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-[#1a1a1a]/5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">
                The Self-Assessment Quiz
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#1a1a1a]/70 leading-relaxed">
                Identify where you are right now: Manual Coordinator, Automation Builder, Agentic Strategist, or AI-Powered Architect. Know your starting point to plan your path forward.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-[#1a1a1a]/5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">
                The Career Insurance Checklist
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#1a1a1a]/70 leading-relaxed">
                The 10 technical skills that make you layoff-resistant in 2026. Plus: which skills to prioritize based on your current role (Scrum Master, Product Owner, RTE, Agile Coach).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-[#1a1a1a]/5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">
                The First 30 Days Roadmap
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#1a1a1a]/70 leading-relaxed">
                Week-by-week action plan to build your first automation system, prove technical value to your team, and start repositioning yourself as an architect (not just a facilitator).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PDF Visual -->
      <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-2xl">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-[#294bf3] to-[#1e3a8a] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center text-white p-6">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold">AI-Powered Agile Blueprint</p>
              <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mt-2">The 3-Phase Transformation</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-center text-[#1a1a1a]/50 text-sm mt-4">Free PDF Guide • Instant Download</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final Closer Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] leading-tight mb-8" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        Your Career Is Too Important to Be Limited by Facilitation Skills.
      </h2>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="text-xl text-[#1a1a1a]/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Whether you've been laid off, fear being replaced by AI, or simply want career optionality instead of job dependency—the path is the same.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-[#1a1a1a]/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Companies aren't cutting agile roles because agile is dead. They're cutting roles that "just coordinate."
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-[#1a1a1a] font-semibold leading-relaxed">
          The professionals who survive and thrive are the ones who can prove they build systems, architect solutions, and create technical value.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xl text-[#294bf3] font-bold mb-10">
        This blueprint is your first step.
      </p>

      <!-- Final CTA -->
      <button
